  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "NPP KlASS Bagariy 防弹胸挂（数码丛林迷彩）",
      "en": "NPP KlASS Bagariy plate carrier (EMR)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Bagariy",
      "en": "Bagariy"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "进入千禧年后，面对不断涌现的全新威胁与任务需求，俄军单兵装备亟待重大变革。为此，俄罗斯军队寻求兼具可靠性与功能性的模块化防弹护甲以满足作战单位对提升防护的需求。2000 年代中期，内务部所属单位（后改组为俄罗斯国民近卫军）率先配发了 Bagariy（巨魾）系列防弹背心。该型护甲不仅列装内卫部队常规单位，还见于特种作战单位。BEAR PMC 们也将其作为主力重型防弹护甲广泛装备。",
      "en": "In the second millennium, the equipment of a soldier received serious changes in view of new threats and tasks. A better level of protection was required, so the Russian army needed a reliable and functional body armor. In the mid-2000s, the MVD, which was later reorganized into the Russian Guard, received Bagariy bulletproof vests. Bagariy was used both by ordinary soldiers of the internal troops, and in special forces. Actively was used by PMC BEAR as the main heavy body armor."
    },
    "weight": 14.2,
    "width": 4,
    "height": 4,
    "rarity": "Superrare",
